Comment 2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Following on Brunner(2002) the authors have chosen to include GDP growth
 and CPI inflation rates in their model.
 I think that in the case of Brunner(2002) that was more appropriate than
 in the case of this manuscript.
 Of course this is just an opinion but the dynamics of the stock market
 prices should be better connected with the Fama French Carhart model variables:
 (see Carhart, M.
