 (1997).
 "On Persistence in Mutual Fund Performance".
 The Journal of Finance.
 52: 57–82.
 doi:10.1111/j.1540-6261.1997.tb03808.x ) monthly premium of the book-to-market
 factor (HML); the monthly premium of the size factor (SMB); and momentum
 of the stock market (UMD).
 These data are all available in WRDS.
\end_layout

